
<div class="center hero-unit">
  <h2>SUL Publications Server</h2>
<hr/>

 <p>Consolidates publication information for Stanford authors.  From here you may browse the profiles for Stanford authors, the PubMed records for those authors, the ScienceWire records, author submitted records, and a consolidated database of all publication sources.You may also query PubMed and ScienceWire directly.</p>
 <p>The consolidated database may also be accessed through it's RESTful API.  The API provides access to Stanford author profile information and the consolidated Stanford publications database.
 </p>

<hr/>

  <h3 style="padding: 5px">
  	RESTful API to SUL Publication Database
  </h3>
  <p> <%= link_to "Browse API Documentation",    static_pages_api_path %></p>

